ion of the ejecta, defined as the ratio between the\nkinetic luminosity $L_{\\rm kin}$ and the radiated luminosity $L_{\\rm rad}$, is\nof the order of one.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Aug 2016 16:23:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-08"}
