avored over\n$w$CDM with a likelihood of $\\approx 92.9\\%-99.6\\%$ versus only $0.4\\%-7.1\\%$.\nThe current HIIGx sample is already large enough for the BIC to rule out\n$\\Lambda$CDM/$w$CDM in favor of $R_{\\rm h}=ct$ at a confidence level\napproaching $3\\sigma$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Aug 2016 06:12:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-24"}
