re shown to\ndepend solely on the mean and variance of the burst-size distribution. Our\nformalism is demonstrated on several realistic distributions which all compare\nwell with numerical Monte-Carlo simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Aug 2016 09:05:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
